column5: Hi     - does anyone know if lake simcoe got hit with the latest snow storm? Last thing it needs is more snow on the ice.    Don
I'm sure misfish or similar Barrie res has a quick answer...but we got no more than 2cm of fluffy stuff up here in Penetang Don. What a change that is!
Thanks Wayne. I am finally gonna get the new hut out Saturday morning and I hope that there isen't much new snow  - adds to the work.   Don
i called a ut operator and he said he didn't have any recent reports as it has been snowing and nobody has been fishing....
in Bradford 8" of snow and 3' drifts  just a few miles south of the lake
